data.description: Spacious  5 BEDROOM older home w/  character & charm offers some nice updating including the large kitchen with multitudes of cabinetry, granite counters & stainless steel appliances!! Downstairs provides kitchen, living & dining areas, 1/2 bath & good size bedroom PLUS full bath. Large lot perfect for entertaining! The back yard features above ground pool w/ deck, covered outdoor cooking area, playhouse & 2 car garage/workshop! Nice front porch w/ accessible balcony above & 2 car carport w/ circle drive.
